
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Index";
}

<h3>Services offered by us</h3>
<p>Our company provides a wide range of professional services designed to meet the needs of 
    businesses and individuals. We focus on delivering high-quality solutions using modern 
    technology and industry best practices. Our team of experts works closely with clients to 
    understand their requirements and provide customized services that help them grow and succeed.</p>
<div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                Web Development
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                We design and develop modern, responsive, and user-friendly websites. Our web development services include website design, front-end and back-end development,
                e-commerce solutions, and website maintenance.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                Mobile Application Development
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Our company develops mobile applications for both Android and iOS platforms. We create secure, fast, and easy-to-use apps that help businesses reach their customers anytime and anywhere.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                Accordion Item #3
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                <strong>This is the third item’s accordion body.</strong> It is hidden by default, until the collapse plugin adds the appropriate classes that we use to style each element. These classes control the overall appearance, as well as the showing and hiding via CSS transitions. You can modify any of this with custom CSS or overriding our default variables. It’s also worth noting that just about any HTML can go within the <code>.accordion-body</code>, though the transition does limit overflow.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


